He thanked me and Doctor Popson.

278
00:20:54,980 --> 00:20:57,310
That is why
he left these two flowers.

279
00:21:04,090 --> 00:21:05,450
Charlie!

280
00:21:11,200 --> 00:21:13,600
Nice job

281
00:21:14,130 --> 00:21:17,140
This is from Charlie's heart.

282
00:21:17,286 --> 00:21:19,940
I have healed his wounded face,

283
00:21:19,940 --> 00:21:23,740
